description: All of Denver is invited to come dig into some delicious BBQ, courtesy of Baby E’s!This big red trailer is hauling in its incredibly tasty hardwood smoked meats straight to the Queen City streets. With sandwiches (like the The Baby E- slow smoked & shredded BBQ pork shoulder piled on a warm Kaiser roll, topped with coleslaw and roasted green chiles), platters, classic sides (like savory baked beans and ooey gooey mac ‘n cheese), and a variety of homemade sauces, all family recipes, Baby E’s is just the best bet when it comes to quality ‘Q. So next time your stomach is grumbling for some scrumptious comfort goodness, you know exactly where to go.
name: Baby E's BBQ
